## 1. Initial Git Setup                                 
### Navigate to your project directory
```bash
cd your-project-folder
```

### Initialize Git repository
```bash
git init
```

## 2. Create .gitignore File

Create a `.gitignore` file in your project root with the following content:

```gitignore
